      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivering power to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed with recent suspension bushing refreshes, and the critical rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced for structural longevity. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the performance envelope remains sharp, offering crisp throttle response and linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing service, ensuring this driver-focused machine is track-ready and street-refined.",
